# Build artefacts that should never land in git.
# release-staging — per CLAUDE.md, where Mike copies the .exe + latest.yml +
# .blockmap before publishing the GitHub Release. Hundreds of MB of binaries
# regenerated from `npm run dist:win`. "Delete staging after" is the rule.
